{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "af862e70-23d6-458b-8558-4a621a43ef5e", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/af862e70-23d6-458b-8558-4a621a43ef5e@1.pkg/1772597700857/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597701048", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/af862e70-23d6-458b-8558-4a621a43ef5e@1.pkg/1772597700857/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597701048"}, "identifier": "af862e70-23d6-458b-8558-4a621a43ef5e", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p align=\"justify\">本题考查正确认识自己。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p align=\"justify\">A“小涵由于孤傲而不愿与人交往，同学提醒，她总是听不进去”，这是不能正确认识他人评价的表现，故A说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">B：“小明参加学校朗诵比赛失利，于是他认为自己什么都不行”，这种行为是没有全面、客观认识自己的表现，故B说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">C：我们可以通过自我评价来认识自己，他人评价有助于我们形成对自己更为客观、完整、清晰的认识，选项中小凯并没有真正认识自己，故C说法错误；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">D：小楠虽然学习成绩不理想，但是她依然坚信好成绩是奋斗出来的，是自信的表现，有助于通过自我评价来增强对自己的信心，更好的发展自己的能力，故D符合题意；</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">故本题选D。</p>\n\n<p align=\"justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p align=\"justify\">2.（改编）正确认识自己对于每个人而言，是一种永恒的主题。下列同学的行为正确的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "2.（改编）正确认识自己对于每个人而言，是一种永恒的主题。下列同学的行为正确的是（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/af862e70-23d6-458b-8558-4a621a43ef5e@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754882300212", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p align=\"justify\">小丽孤傲而且不愿与人交往，父母提醒，但她依旧没有改变</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>小明参加学校朗诵比赛失利，于是他认为自己什么也干不了</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>班级组建篮球队，小凯认为自己的球技最棒，当队长最合适</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p align=\"justify\">小楠虽然成绩不理想，但是她依然坚信好成绩是奋斗出来的</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p align=\"justify\">2.（改编）正确认识自己对于每个人而言，是一种永恒的主题。下列同学的行为正确的是（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "af862e70-23d6-458b-8558-4a621a43ef5e", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "2.（改编）正确认识自己对于每个人而言